_sText: race_shitter_derby Probably my most fun race map so far, this is race_shitter_derby. Complete two laps to finish the race. Be careful with turbo though because you might flip your buggy going over the bumps in this map. As with all rally race maps this can not be used to play regular CS:S -- there are no bomb sites or hostages. This map is only for use with a Rally Race server. Questions or comments? Feel free to talk to PM me or leave them here.
